    <h2>How GrubClub Works</h2>
    <h3>Process Outline:</h3>

    <ol>
        <li>Complete the Grub Club set-up form. <a href="#">Click here to create a Grub Club</a></li>
        <li>If your Grub Club is approved, we will let you know so you can start marketing your event to your followers</li>
        <li>The Grub Club event URL will be the link you need to use in your marketing materials, so people can book places and pay for your events, e.g. <a href="http://grubclub.com/quintoquarto">grubclub.com/quintoquarto</a>
        <li>Keep a regular check on your bookings and your guests’ dietary requirements which are specified at the point of booking (see Admin section below)</li>
    </ol>

    <p>If you need help with anything, please let us know! We are very happy to help you look for volunteer swaps, venues, collaborations, produce, etc. Just ask and we’ll be very happy to chat with you.</p>

